{"tid":219117,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"2017年香港平均加薪3.9%　IT、地產及物管加最多","createTime":"2017-04-27T03:58:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-27T11:11:19.000Z","uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c9ae17f41464da659f3ee3550fecb0d4f13b746d","tid":219117,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T03:58:32.000Z","msg":"據jobsDB最新的「2017年薪酬調查報告」顯示，香港僱員今年平均獲加薪3.9%。<br />\n<br />\n這項薪酬調查發現，本年「資訊科技」及「地產及物業管理」從業員的薪酬增長幅度最高。不過對大部分受訪者來說，「轉工」仍然是增加收入的最佳途徑之一。<br />\n<br />\n雖然2017年的平均薪酬增長略高於去年的3.6%，但仍然顯著低於2015年的4.7%，並遠遠低於2014年的5.9%。<br />\n<br />\njobsDB香港總經理饒志文表示：「據政府預測，2017年香港約有2至3%的經濟增長，相信本港僱員的薪酬亦因而隨之略為上調；至於來季市場的表現則取決於下半年度的全球經濟活動。」<br />\n<br />\n全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.jobsdb.com/en-hk/articles/2017%E5%B9%B4%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%B9%B3%E5%9D%87%E5%8A%A0%E8%96%AA3-9-it-%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E5%8F%8A%E7%89%A9%E7%AE%A1%E5%8A%A0%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%9A?utm_campaign=c%3Aicbb_enewsc_1704b%3A20170426&amp;utm_source=edm&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_content=link3_survey\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.jobsdb.com%2Fen-hk%2Farticles%2F2017%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E5%259D%2587%25E5%258A%25A0%25E8%2596%25AA3-9-it-%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25A2%25E5%258F%258A%25E7%2589%25A9%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E5%258A%25A0%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25A4%259A%3Futm_campaign%3Dc%253Aicbb_enewsc_1704b%253A20170426%26utm_source%3Dedm%26utm_medium%3Demail%26utm_content%3Dlink3_survey&d=uo2GI0poDlFkSsUZ5iwE4hxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=9b21c860\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.jobsdb.com/en-hk/articles/2017%E5%B9%B4%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%B9%B3%E5%9D%87%E5%8A%A0%E8%96%AA3-9-it-%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E5%8F%8A%E7%89%A9%E7%AE%A1%E5%8A%A0%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%9A?utm_campaign=c%3Aicbb_enewsc_1704b%3A20170426&amp;utm_source=edm&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_content=link3_survey</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nIT <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"569e646c1a6123ee99dbac8b4683402da87af5c9","t